                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8190" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0107</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3022 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">走心走实--ZX教育高级客户经理的营销沟通之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Walking from Heart to Reality - The Marketing Communication Path of ZX Education Senior Account Manager</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马玉，王桀，胡淑婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曾萍</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中旭教育</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业培训；营销；沟通</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Enterprise training; Marketing; communicate</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">用心了解、切实满足客户需求是企业生存之本，发展之源。而客户需求的精准识别，共同价值的有效挖掘离不开双方信息、思想和情感的传递与交流。沟通是连接企业与市场之间的重要桥梁。营销即沟通，成功的营销离不开高效的沟通。ZX教育是一家培训咨询企业，本案例以 ZX 教育高级客户经理李清拜访 NT 物流相关领导的过程为主线，描述了面对陌生客户，李清如何以真诚和专业，增进了解，赢得信任，展现价值，推动销售成功的过程；揭示了营销过程的四个基本阶段，即集中顾客注意力、引发顾客兴趣、激发顾客购买欲望和促进顾客购买行为；展现了沟通活动的三项重要技巧：引导式提问、深度倾听以及正面反馈。本案例旨在加深学生对管理沟通理论的掌握，启发学生对“AIDA”营销模型的理解，加强学生对沟通客体策略、营销沟通技巧的运用，为企业开展高效的营销沟通提供一定理论启示与实践借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Understanding and meeting customer needs is the foundation of enterprise survival and development. The precise identification of customer needs and the effective exploration of common value cannot be achieved without sufficient communication of information, ideas, and emotions between both parties. Communication is an important bridge connecting enterprises and the market. Marketing is communication, effective communication is essential for successful marketing. ZX Education is a training and consulting enterprise. This case focuses on the process of Li Qing, a senior account manager of ZX Education, visiting NT logistics related leaders. It describes how the account manager, with sincerity and professionalism, enhances understanding, wins trust, showcases value, and promotes sales success in the face of unfamiliar customers. It reveals four stages in the marketing process: focusing customer attention, arousing customer interest, stimulating customer purchasing desire and promoting customer purchasing behavior. It demonstrates the practice of three communication skills: guided questioning, deep listening, and positive feedback. This case aims to deepen students&#39; grasp of management communication theory, inspire their understanding of  “AIDA” marketing model, strengthen their application of object oriented communication strategies and marketing communication skills, and provide theoretical inspiration and practical reference for enterprises to carry out efficient marketing communication.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理沟通》、《商务礼仪》、《营销沟通》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">沟通客体策略；商务沟通礼仪；营销沟通</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-03</td>
                            </tr>
